  <scopecontent id="aspace_ebf5d8a2ef8e4e643721be56456631cc">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Albums of photographs of famous personages in the arts. Some photographs are formal head and shoulder type, others are full length. Many are of actors portrayed in the roles they played in well known plays. One volume is an alphabetical index to the photograph albums.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <arrangement id="aspace_939c539955d3ab20fd3ddf3918d8deb4">
    <head>COLLECTION ARRANGEMENT</head>
<p>There are twenty-six volumes labelled A-Z and twenty-nine volumes numbered 1-29, as well as an index volume. The index volume is alphabetical and gives the letter or number of the volume in which the photographs may be found. They are not in any particular order in the volume.</p>  </arrangement>
